title: Overhaul Share Activity/Service for token use
message:
Overhaul Share Activity/Service for token use

Also Changes to settings to handle the case when no token has been set
or the set token is invalid and ShareActivity calls settings

Shared image is now saved to the application cache directory since some
forms of sharing with ContentProvider have a very narrow permission
scope, cache is cleaned for old images (30 minutes) and the image is
deleted after it is done being uploaded
